	eting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required.\n\nDeta
	iled Description: Early Learning is a great way for kids ages 0-5 and thei
	r families to develop learning\, literacy\, and language skills as well as
	 community with other families.\, We read stories\, sing songs\, and have 
	engaging\, educational activities that help kids and their caregivers grow
	 together.\n\nEvent Logistics: Registration is not required but these prog
	rams are very popular and the room capacity can fill up quickly.\, Familie
	s of all ages are welcome\, though this early learning program is intended
	 for youth aged 0-5\, their caregivers and families.\, Doors to the meetin
	g room will open at 6:40 p.m. This is a flat\, stroller-friendly entrance 
	on 4th Ave W.\, The entrance to the meeting room from the Library is down 
	a flight of stairs.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n
	\nprograms.\n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk
