DESCRIPTION:Earlybirds Club is a dance party designed for women\, trans\, a
	nd non-binary folks that starts at 6pm and ends at 10pm - because we have 
	shit to do in the morning!Our DJ spins music from the 80s to 2000s\, inclu
	ding pop\, hip-hop\, new wave\, and Rs home! Earlybirds Club is more than 
	a fun night out\, its a supportive space where kindness\, good vibes\, and
	 sensible footwear rule\, and 10% of proceeds always benefit a local non-p
	rofit. Come as you are - theres plenty of room on the dance floor for ever
	yone.10% of ticket proceeds benefit Womens Reproductive Rights Assistance 
	Project\, which assists women who are financially unable to pay for safe\,
	 legal abortions or emergency contraception.Note: By purchasing these tick
	ets\, you are consenting to be photographed for promotional purposes. Peop
	le of all backgrounds and identities are encouraged to attend all of our e
